projects.name: Chess Game Using Genetic Algorithm
projects.description: Developed a fully autonomous chess game utilizing a genetic algorithm, where chess pieces move independently based on the algorithms strategic decisions. The algorithm iteratively conducts selection, crossover, mutation, and replacement processes across a predened number of generations or until a convergence criterion is achieved, ultimately terminating when a satisfactory solution is identied.
